    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一片废墟的海洋中醒来，失去了记忆。为了生存而战，探索危机四伏的荒原，找回真正的自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exsys 是一款动作冒险游戏，融合了经典的 90 年代清版动作游戏玩法和现代动作 RPG 元素。探索充满废墟和危险的迷人 3D 世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由连击系统： 摆脱僵化的连招！在自由流畅的战斗中释放毁灭性的连击。通过组合攻击和指令，创造你独特的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主动技能系统： 以可装备物品的形式发现技能。混合搭配以定制你的战斗风格。使用格斗游戏风格的指令来释放它们的力量。 混合、匹配和排序具有相同指令的技能，以创建按顺序执行的连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品系统： 收集和利用各种物品来增强你的属性，削弱敌人，并释放特殊攻击。在战斗中最多装备 4 件物品，以便快速使用。结合物品和技能，创造独特的战斗风格，并在残酷的废墟世界中生存下来。 将物品存放在仓库中，供你的下一个角色使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的角色只有一条命。如果你的角色死亡，你将失去该角色的所有物品，</p></li></ul>",
